verbose_text: However, unlike its response to AMB, there was no difference in level of sensitivity of the A. flavus CA14msnADelta mutant and the parental strain to ITZ (i.e., MICs for both strains were between 0.25 and 0.5 mug mL -1; although, some discoloration of the parental strain occurred with ITZ treatment; Figure XREF_FIG).
